{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM03_ST2_540.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x27,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "...t's my story, and I thought that maybe you knew about more rare books..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xf5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*sniff*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Wh-Wh-Why did you start crying all of a sudden!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xf7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh, no no, excuse me. I'm so happy, I was moved to tears..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "How magnificent it is that you have come to depend on me. Nothing like this has ever happened to me before!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "No one in Vierzeberg has shown even the slightest interest in the ruins of ancient civilizations."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "But, you're different. I always knew you were a promising child!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x24,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "To honor your ambition and intellectual curiosity, I'll do whatever I can to help."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Wow! Thank you so much!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x56,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Now then, first of all, about that book you have, it's about one type of alchemy that became popular long ago..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5e,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "A book that recounts the secret art of Anciemy!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "An...ciemy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x58,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "The technique of turning precious metals into base metals!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Through mystical means, it allows the creation of various things through a process called synthesis..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "That is the art! Isn't Anciemy wonderful!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Indeed, it's written in an ancient language, so even my superior brain can't quite comprehend it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb0,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "It's really disappointing. If I could decipher that book, it would be a major breakthrough for my research!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Umm, Mr. Harry, do you have any other books like that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb1,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Of course! I had lots of them. Though it's a shame that I have to point out that the operative word is \"had\"..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb6,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "But, they were all so complex that I lost my patience and threw‐er, gave them all away."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat? Everything!? Wh-What a waste..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "But don't fret. They may be historically rare documents, but there are ways to obtain them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "If you truly have such aspirations, then I will be most generous with my cooperation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "...Although, with so many books, obtaining them all will undoubtedly be very difficult."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Difficult...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "To the south lies a deserted village. It is said that all of its inhabitants have disappeared."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Further south beyond that village lies a dense forest, where it's always dark, even during the day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Following the road even further will lead you past the vast marshland and eventually to Hornheim..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "But it's dangerous if you stray from the road, because of all the wild beasts that infest the surrounding areas..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Umm...what are you talking about? It doesn't seem like that has anything to do with books..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Just listen, if you travel down that path without a path, you might find a strange mansion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "The mistress of that mansion lives alone, surrounded by a massive amount of books."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "A massive amount of books...? Then, the book I'm looking for..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "There is a strong possibility. Of course, I've never been there myself, so I don't know any specific details."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "But, it certainly is a dangerous journey. It's no place for a girl like you to go..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "You're right... I'll try to find a better way..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "That's good. If it comes down to it, I'll organize a caravan."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "There's no way you'll ever be disappointed if you come to me for help."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "(Yup, it was a good idea to come ask Mr. Harry!)"
        }
    ]
}